Two figures in [[hyperbolic space|Hyperbolic geometry]] $$H^n$$ are //congruent// if they are related by an [[orthogonal transformation|Orthogonale Gruppen]] $$A\in \O^+(n,1),$$ which is the isometry group of $$H^n.$$